title: Ep. 1177 - Jetha Splattered With Mud - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal screams looking at Jetha's condition. He asks him to go out and get it cleaned before he enters the house. Iyer clicks a photo of Jetha cleaning his body and tells him that he will be showing this to everyone in the society.

title: Ep. 1178 - Anjali Is Suspicious - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak comes home late and soon gets a call. Anjali asks him about who is calling him so late. She finds out that he has already had his dinner and didn't even think of informing her about it.

title: Ep. 1179 - Taarak Makes Way For Suspicion - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali asks Taarak to take a bath and he takes his laptop with him. She asks him if he wants to destroy the laptop and tries to take it from him, he runs around with it. Taarak talks to a girl on social media and writes poetry for her.

title: Ep 1180 - Anjali Breaks Down
shortDesc: When Daya asks Anjali the reason behind her sadness, she breaks down. Crying, she tells Daya that Taarak has another woman in his life. Daya is shocked and pacifies her.

title: Ep. 1181 - Daya Sympathizes With Anjali - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali cries and tells Daya as how much she loves Taarak. She regrets making him eat all the diet and less oily food. Daya tells her not to cry and wash her face, she will feel fresh. Anjali overhears Daya and Jetha's conversation that Taarak had lie

title: Ep. 1182 - Jethalal Lies To Champaklal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal informs Anjali and Daya that Champaklal has come. He sins devotional song to impress Champaklal and asks him to come to the balcony if he wants to hear more of it. Anjali sneaks into their home with the help of Daya.

title: Ep. 1183 - Jethalal Is Shocked - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal spots Taarak with a girl. He thinks of confronting him but they went off. He decides to reveal the truth to Champaklal, Anjali and Daya about Taarak's new relationship. Anjali and Jetha tell their part of story to Champaklal.

title: Ep. 1184 - The Misconception - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: To everyone's surprise, Kavita claims Taarak as her brother. Taarak clears the air and reveals the truth as what had exactly happened for which he had to hide all this from everyone.

title: Ep. 1185 - Football In Rain - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu asks Jetha for money to buy a football as they want play it during the rain. Jetha refuses and says rather they should be playing cricket. Tapu convinces, Jetha gives in and warns him not to create any nuisance.

title: Ep. 1186 - Bhide's Carom Skills - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Popatlal play carom board and Bhide is really good at it. The kids come and appreciate Popatlal for helping them. Tapu informs Jetha that he has given his number to some internet quiz competition.

title: Ep. 1187 - Daya's Drama - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya welcomes Jetha they making him tea and snacks. She acts like a queen and enacts a scene. Jetha joins her in the act.

title: Ep. 1188 - The Notice - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Popatlal inform Tarak and Iyer about the notice received in the society. Everyone is very stressed out and gather for a meeting. What is the notice about?

title: Ep. 1189 - No Trespassing - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After the notice was issued, The government places a no trespassing board in front of the society gate. Roshan and the others gets furious and starts arguing with the workers.

title: Ep. 1190 - The Court Case - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the men from Gokuldham return from the police station and head to Tarak's place to discuss the situation. They tell Champaklal that the lawyers and asking a hefty fee. How will Gokuldham handle this situation.

title: Ep. 1191 - The Terms And Conditions - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal tells the lawyer that He'll somehow arrange the money and give him. The lawyer trusts Champaklal and lays out his terms and conditions. Will they abide by the rules?
